@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bpomlv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.64 / v0 + 0.68) / (v0 + 0.53 / tmp + 0.34)) + ((tmp + 0.56 * tmp + 0.64) + tmp))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.81)) / wp.abs((v1 + 0.36 * tmp + 0.51)))
    v0 = 0.28
    data[tid] = v0
